{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01X5MGk2evkgm4qCC3F7gqR6","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the information I need. Let me compile the comprehensive inventory report.\n\n## Challenge Engine Database & Test Implementation Inventory\n\n---\n\n### 1. MIGRATION FILE: Database Schema\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/migrations/011_challenge_engine.sql`\n\n#### CREATE TABLE Statements with Constraints:\n\n| Table Name | Line | Key Constraints & Indexes |\n|-----------|------|--------------------------|\n| `reward_config` | 4-8 | PRIMARY KEY: `key` (TEXT), DEFAULT `updated_at` = now() |\n| `player_points` | 11-17 | PRIMARY KEY: `user_id` (TEXT), UNIQUE: `wallet`, DEFAULT `balance` = 0, DEFAULT `lifetime_earned` = 0 |\n| `point_grants` | 20-30 | PRIMARY KEY: `id` (BIGINT IDENTITY), UNIQUE: `(user_id, source_type, source_id)`, CHECK `source_type` IN (...), INDEX: `idx_point_grants_user_created` |\n| `reward_pool` | 35-41 | PRIMARY KEY: `id` (1 singleton), CHECK `id = 1`, DEFAULT `balance_lamports` = 0, DEFAULT `lifetime_funded` = 0 |\n| `reward_pool_fundings` | 44-50 | PRIMARY KEY: `id` (BIGINT IDENTITY), UNIQUE: `round_id` |\n| `campaigns` | 53-62 | PRIMARY KEY: `id` (BIGINT IDENTITY), UNIQUE: `name`, CHECK `campaign_type` IN ('daily', 'weekly', 'onboarding', 'dogpile'), DEFAULT `is_active` = true |\n| `challenges` | 65-81 | PRIMARY KEY: `id` (BIGINT IDENTITY), FOREIGN KEY: `campaign_id`, FOREIGN KEY: `prerequisite_id` (self-ref), CHECK `scope` IN ('any', 'coinflip', 'lord', 'closecall'), CHECK `reward_type` IN ('points', 'crate'), DEFAULT `is_active` = true |\n| `challenge_assignments` | 84-96 | PRIMARY KEY: `id` (BIGINT IDENTITY), FOREIGN KEY: `challenge_id`, UNIQUE: `(user_id, challenge_id, period_key)`, CHECK `status` IN ('active', 'completed', 'expired'), INDEX: `idx_assignments_active` (WHERE status='active'), INDEX: `idx_assignments_period` |\n| `progress_events` | 102-111 | PRIMARY KEY: `id` (BIGINT IDENTITY), FOREIGN KEY: `assignment_id`, UNIQUE: `(assignment_id, round_id)` |\n| `completion_bonuses` | 114-124 | PRIMARY KEY: `id` (BIGINT IDENTITY), FOREIGN KEY: `campaign_id`, CHECK `reward_type` IN ('points', 'crate') |\n| `bonus_completions` | 127-134 | PRIMARY KEY: `id` (BIGINT IDENTITY), FOREIGN KEY: `bonus_id`, UNIQUE: `(user_id, bonus_id, period_key)` |\n| `crate_drops` | 137-148 | PRIMARY KEY: `id` (BIGINT IDENTITY), CHECK `trigger_type` IN (...), CHECK `crate_type` IN ('points', 'sol'), CHECK `status` IN ('pending', 'granted', 'failed'), UNIQUE: `(user_id, trigger_type, trigger_id)`, INDEX: `idx_crate_drops_user`, INDEX: `idx_crate_drops_pending` |\n| `fraud_flags` | 154-163 | PRIMARY KEY: `id` (BIGINT IDENTITY), DEFAULT `status` = 'open', CHECK `status` IN ('open', 'reviewed', 'dismissed') |\n| `dogpile_events` | 166-174 | PRIMARY KEY: `id` (BIGINT IDENTITY), FOREIGN KEY: `campaign_id` (optional), CHECK `status` IN ('scheduled', 'active', 'ended', 'cancelled'), INDEX: `idx_dogpile_active` |\n\n---\n\n### 2. SEED DATA\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/migrations/011_challenge_engine.sql` (Lines 182-239)\n\n#### reward_config Defaults (Lines 183-194):\n- `points_per_dollar` = '500'\n- `dogpile_default_multiplier` = '2.0'\n- `reward_pool_fee_share` = '0.20'\n- `points_crate_drop_rate` = '0.05'\n- `sol_crate_drop_rate` = '0.01'\n- `sol_crate_pool_pct` = '0.10'\n- `sol_crate_min_value` = '10000000'\n- `points_crate_min` = '500'\n- `points_crate_max` = '5000'\n- `daily_challenge_count` = '3'\n- `weekly_challenge_count` = '2'\n\n#### reward_pool Singleton (Line 197):\n- Single row: `id=1, balance_lamports=0, lifetime_funded=0, lifetime_paid=0`\n\n#### Campaigns (Lines 200-203):\n- **Daily Challenges** (campaign_type: 'daily')\n- **Weekly Challenges** (campaign_type: 'weekly')\n- **Onboarding** (campaign_type: 'onboarding')\n\n#### Daily Challenges (Lines 206-212):\n6 challenge templates inserted, with sort_order 1-6:\n1. \"Play 3 Games\" (3 threshold, 100 points) — sort_order 1\n2. \"Win a Coinflip\" (1 threshold, 150 points, scope=coinflip) — sort_order 2\n3. \"Fill a Lobby\" (1 threshold, 200 points) — sort_order 3\n4. \"Play 5 Games\" (5 threshold, 250 points) — sort_order 4\n5. \"Win 3 Games\" (3 threshold, 300 points) — sort_order 5\n6. \"Try Close Call\" (1 threshold, 150 points, scope=closecall) — sort_order 6\n\n#### Weekly Challenges (Lines 215-219):\n4 challenge templates, sort_order 1-4:\n1. \"Play 20 Games\" (20 threshold, 1000 points)\n2. \"Win 10 Games\" (10 threshold, 1500 points)\n3. \"Play Every Game Type\" (unique_game_types condition, 3 threshold, 2000 points)\n4. \"Fill 5 Lobbies\" (5 threshold, 1200 points)\n\n#### Onboarding Chain (Lines 221-234):\n3-step prerequisite chain:\n1. \"Play Your First Game\" (1 threshold, 1000 points) — sort_order 1, no prerequisite\n2. \"Win a Game\" (1 threshold, 1500 points) — sort_order 2, prerequisite = step 1\n3. \"Try All 3 Game Types\" (unique_game_types, 3 threshold, 2500 points) — sort_order 3, prerequisite = step 2\n\n#### Completion Bonus (Lines 237-238):\n- **Daily Bonus Crate**: Complete all 3 daily challenges → 'crate' reward\n\n---\n\n### 3. INTEGRATION TESTS\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/__tests__/integration.test.ts`\n\n#### Describe Block: \"Integration: create → join → settle lifecycle\" (Line 290)\n*Note: This is the main lifecycle test suite, which includes challenge engine tests below*\n\n#### Challenge Engine Related Tests:\n\n**GAME_SETTLED handler (orchestrator)** — Lines 1762-2423:\n- Line 1766: `it(\"game.settled handler: processes challenge progress + emits reward events\")`\n- Line 1828: `it(\"game.settled handler: completes challenge + emits reward intent when target reached\")`\n- Line 1887: `it(\"game.settled handler: skips refunded game (isWinner === null)\")`\n- Line 1943: `it(\"game.settled handler: idempotent — same event twice produces no double progress\")`\n- Line 1991: `it(\"game.settled handler: completion bonus awarded when all daily challenges completed\")`\n- Line 2074: `it(\"game.settled handler: completion bonus is idempotent — no duplicate on re-trigger\")`\n- Line 2135: `it(\"game.settled handler: no bonus when only 2 of 3 daily challenges completed\")`\n- Line 2216: `it(\"game.settled handler: completing onboarding step 1 auto-assigns step 2\")`\n- Line 2282: `it(\"game.settled handler: completing all 3 onboarding steps creates no further assignment\")`\n- Line 2348: `it(\"game.settled handler: onboarding chain progression is idempotent per assignment\")`\n\n---\n\n#### Describe Block: \"GET /challenges/mine\" (Line 2429)\n- Line 2459: `it(\"first call creates 3 daily + 2 weekly + 1 onboarding assignment, returns correct shape\")`\n- Line 2532: `it(\"second call returns same assignments (no duplicates)\")`\n- Line 2559: `it(\"expired assignments are marked expired\")`\n\n---\n\n#### Describe Block: \"GET /points/mine + /points/mine/history + /crates/mine\" (Line 2598)\n- Line 2636: `it(\"GET /points/mine returns zeros when no player_points row exists\")`\n- Line 2648: `it(\"GET /points/mine returns balance and lifetimeEarned from player_points\")`\n- Line 2666: `it(\"GET /points/mine/history returns paginated point_grants with cursor\")`\n- Line 2708: `it(\"GET /points/mine/history returns empty array when no grants\")`\n- Line 2720: `it(\"GET /crates/mine returns paginated crate_drops with cursor\")`\n- Line 2771: `it(\"GET /crates/mine returns empty array when no crate drops\")`\n\n---\n\n#### Describe Block: \"GET /challenges/mine/history + /dogpile/current + /dogpile/schedule\" (Line 2788)\n- Line 2824: `it(\"GET /challenges/mine/history returns paginated completed assignments\")`\n- Line 2867: `it(\"GET /challenges/mine/history returns empty when no completed assignments\")`\n- Line 2890: `it(\"GET /dogpile/current returns active event over scheduled\")`\n- Line 2915: