isite chain:\n1. \"Play Your First Game\" (1 threshold, 1000 points) — sort_order 1, no prerequisite\n2. \"Win a Game\" (1 threshold, 1500 points) — sort_order 2, prerequisite = step 1\n3. \"Try All 3 Game Types\" (unique_game_types, 3 threshold, 2500 points) — sort_order 3, prerequisite = step 2\n\n#### Completion Bonus (Lines 237-238):\n- **Daily Bonus Crate**: Complete all 3 daily challenges → 'crate' reward\n\n---\n\n### 3. INTEGRATION TESTS\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/__tests__/integration.test.ts`\n\n#### Describe Block: \"Integration: create → join → settle lifecycle\" (Line 290)\n*Note: This is the main lifecycle test suite, which includes challenge engine tests below*\n\n#### Challenge Engine Related Tests:\n\n**GAME_SETTLED handler (orchestrator)** — Lines 1762-2423:\n- Line 1766: `it(\"game.settled handler: processes challenge progress + emits reward events\")`\n- Line 1828: `it(\"game.settled handler: completes challenge + emits reward intent when target reached\")`\n- Line 1887: `it(\"game.settled handler: skips refunded game (isWinner === null)\")`\n- Line 1943: `it(\"game.settled handler: idempotent — same event twice produces no double progress\")`\n- Line 1991: `it(\"game.settled handler: completion bonus awarded when all daily challenges completed\")`\n- Line 2074: `it(\"game.settled handler: completion bonus is idempotent — no duplicate on re-trigger\")`\n- Line 2135: `it(\"game.settled handler: no bonus when only 2 of 3 daily challenges completed\")`\n- Line 2216: `it(\"game.settled handler: completing onboarding step 1 auto-assigns step 2\")`\n- Line 2282: `it(\"game.settled handler: completing all 3 onboarding steps creates no further assignment\")`\n- Line 2348: `it(\"game.settled handler: onboarding chain progression is idempotent per assignment\")`\n\n---\n\n#### Describe Block: \"GET /challenges/mine\" (Line 2429)\n- Line 2459: `it(\"first call creates 3 daily + 2 weekly + 1 onboarding assignment, retur